another large group of people.

48
00:03:15,195 --> 00:03:18,990
<i>I wouldn't want to be like Mike.
It's an impossible task.</i>

49
00:03:21,618 --> 00:03:23,244
Yeah, this is not...

50
00:03:24,370 --> 00:03:26,623
