- You can beat that.
- In four tries. Come back here.

110
00:06:39,982 --> 00:06:42,068
- Give him his...
- Hey, Gus, CT.

111
00:06:43,986 --> 00:06:48,449
Hey, man, your stuff rolls.
He's out here, it just rolls up there.

112
00:06:48,533 --> 00:06:50,660
Watch this roll
right into my pocket.

113
00:06:51,744 --> 00:06:53,996
- I got good at this.
- Y'all get out of here.

114
00:06:54,080 --> 00:06:55,957
Go protect the damn United Center.

115
