Hey, Mike. Hey, Scottie.

118
00:07:10,596 --> 00:07:12,432
- Okay, my brother.
- This guy's funny.

119
00:07:12,515 --> 00:07:15,726
- I'm sure you have full season tickets.
- You guys know the money man here?

120
00:07:15,810 --> 00:07:17,228
Yeah, we know him.

